{"code": "RULE-DDX-9FF8EF625B0D", "id": "RULE-DDX-9FF8EF625B0D", "name": "冠状动脉痉挛与固定冠脉狭窄鉴别规则", "preferred_name": "冠状动脉痉挛与固定冠脉狭窄鉴别规则", "display_name": "冠状动脉痉挛与固定冠脉狭窄鉴别规则", "entityType": "ClinicalRule", "entityCategory": "CDSS决策规则", "canonical_labels": ["KGNode", "ClinicalRule"], "primary_label": "ClinicalRule", "type_label": "鉴别规则", "rule_category": "differential_point", "rule_type": "鉴别诊断规则", "rule_text": "出现心肌缺血症状但冠脉造影/CTA未提示固定心外膜冠脉狭窄时，应考虑冠状动脉痉挛或微血管病变；其与稳定粥样硬化固定狭窄导致的冠心病表型不同，需结合发作特点、动态心电图、冠脉功能评估和抗痉挛治疗反应鉴别。", "original_text": "出现心肌缺血症状但冠脉造影/CTA未提示固定心外膜冠脉狭窄时，应考虑冠状动脉痉挛或微血管病变；其与稳定粥样硬化固定狭窄导致的冠心病表型不同，需结合发作特点、动态心电图、冠脉功能评估和抗痉挛治疗反应鉴别。", "evidence_note": "教材明确指出CCS心肌缺血多由固定狭窄诱发，但冠脉痉挛或微血管病变可无心外膜固定狭窄。", "differential_target_code": "DDX-CARD-A4091D292E4B", "differential_target_name": "冠状动脉痉挛", "source_disease_codes": ["DIS-CARD-CAD-CCS", "DIS-CARD-CAD-NSTEMI", "DIS-CARD-CAD-AMI", "DIS-CARD-CAD-ACS", "DIS-CARD-CAD-UA", "DIS-CARD-CAD-STABLE-ANGINA", "DIS-CARD-CAD-STEMI"], "source_disease_names": ["慢性冠脉综合征", "非ST段抬高型心肌梗死", "急性心肌梗死", "急性冠脉综合征", "不稳定型心绞痛", "稳定型心绞痛", "ST段抬高型心肌梗死"], "scope_type": "心血管内科", "scope_target": "真实鉴别对象规则补齐", "top_specialty": "心血管内科", "batch_id": "BATCH-CARD-DDX-RULE-FILL-20260714-001", "schema_version": "V1.12", "skill_version": "V2.1", "source_type": "authoritative_textbook_or_guideline", "knowledge_layer": "differential_diagnosis_detail", "skeleton_slot": "诊断与鉴别诊断", "clinical_applicability": "diagnosis_support", "review_status": "clinical_ready", "clinical_review_status": "clinical_ready", "formal_cdss_ready": "yes", "merge_status": "server_imported", "conflict_status": "none", "created_at": "2026-07-14 09:58:05", "updated_at": "2026-07-14 09:58:05", "evidence_codes": ["EVD-TB-084D561AEA10CE9D4B47-CCS"]}
{"code": "RULE-DDX-2ADEA00FEA49", "id": "RULE-DDX-2ADEA00FEA49", "name": "STEMI与嗜铬细胞瘤鉴别规则", "preferred_name": "STEMI与嗜铬细胞瘤鉴别规则", "display_name": "STEMI与嗜铬细胞瘤鉴别规则", "entityType": "ClinicalRule", "entityCategory": "CDSS决策规则", "canonical_labels": ["KGNode", "ClinicalRule"], "primary_label": "ClinicalRule", "type_label": "鉴别规则", "rule_category": "differential_point", "rule_type": "鉴别诊断规则", "rule_text": "STEMI疑似场景如伴头痛、心悸、出汗、血压剧烈波动或收缩压显著升高后骤降，应鉴别嗜铬细胞瘤；嗜铬细胞瘤可因儿茶酚胺大量释放导致冠脉弥漫性收缩、ST段改变和心肌坏死标志物升高，但冠脉常无狭窄病变，需结合腹部影像及血/尿儿茶酚胺和代谢产物。", "original_text": "STEMI疑似场景如伴头痛、心悸、出汗、血压剧烈波动或收缩压显著升高后骤降，应鉴别嗜铬细胞瘤；嗜铬细胞瘤可因儿茶酚胺大量释放导致冠脉弥漫性收缩、ST段改变和心肌坏死标志物升高，但冠脉常无狭窄病变，需结合腹部影像及血/尿儿茶酚胺和代谢产物。", "evidence_note": "教材STEMI鉴别诊断段落包含嗜铬细胞瘤鉴别要点。", "differential_target_code": "DDX-CARD-STEMI-BED7C76BD0A8", "differential_target_name": "嗜铬细胞瘤", "source_disease_codes": ["DIS-CARD-CAD-STEMI"], "source_disease_names": ["ST段抬高型心肌梗死"], "scope_type": "心血管内科", "scope_target": "真实鉴别对象规则补齐", "top_specialty": "心血管内科", "batch_id": "BATCH-CARD-DDX-RULE-FILL-20260714-001", "schema_version": "V1.12", "skill_version": "V2.1", "source_type": "authoritative_textbook_or_guideline", "knowledge_layer": "differential_diagnosis_detail", "skeleton_slot": "诊断与鉴别诊断", "clinical_applicability": "diagnosis_support", "review_status": "clinical_ready", "clinical_review_status": "clinical_ready", "formal_cdss_ready": "yes", "merge_status": "server_imported", "conflict_status": "none", "created_at": "2026-07-14 09:58:05", "updated_at": "2026-07-14 09:58:05", "evidence_codes": ["EVD-TB-E70DF8CB7C3CA076A861-AMI"]}
{"code": "RULE-DDX-B95FE741EED1", "id": "RULE-DDX-B95FE741EED1", "name": "STEMI与心绞痛鉴别规则", "preferred_name": "STEMI与心绞痛鉴别规则", "display_name": "STEMI与心绞痛鉴别规则", "entityType": "ClinicalRule", "entityCategory": "CDSS决策规则", "canonical_labels": ["KGNode", "ClinicalRule"], "primary_label": "ClinicalRule", "type_label": "鉴别规则", "rule_category": "differential_point", "rule_type": "鉴别诊断规则", "rule_text": "胸痛患者需区分心绞痛与AMI/STEMI：心绞痛多为暂时性心肌缺血而无坏死，疼痛持续较短且硝酸甘油常可缓解；AMI/STEMI为持续严重缺血导致心肌坏死，疼痛更持久，常伴心肌坏死标志物升高和特征性/动态性心电图变化。", "original_text": "胸痛患者需区分心绞痛与AMI/STEMI：心绞痛多为暂时性心肌缺血而无坏死，疼痛持续较短且硝酸甘油常可缓解；AMI/STEMI为持续严重缺血导致心肌坏死，疼痛更持久，常伴心肌坏死标志物升高和特征性/动态性心电图变化。", "evidence_note": "教材指出两者本质区别为缺血程度不同，并给出疼痛、硝酸甘油反应、坏死标志物和心电图鉴别要点。", "differential_target_code": "DDX-CARD-STEMI-4DD215C51903", "differential_target_name": "心绞痛", "source_disease_codes": ["DIS-CARD-CAD-STEMI"], "source_disease_names": ["ST段抬高型心肌梗死"], "scope_type": "心血管内科", "scope_target": "真实鉴别对象规则补齐", "top_specialty": "心血管内科", "batch_id": "BATCH-CARD-DDX-RULE-FILL-20260714-001", "schema_version": "V1.12", "skill_version": "V2.1", "source_type": "authoritative_textbook_or_guideline", "knowledge_layer": "differential_diagnosis_detail", "skeleton_slot": "诊断与鉴别诊断", "clinical_applicability": "diagnosis_support", "review_status": "clinical_ready", "clinical_review_status": "clinical_ready", "formal_cdss_ready": "yes", "merge_status": "server_imported", "conflict_status": "none", "created_at": "2026-07-14 09:58:05", "updated_at": "2026-07-14 09:58:05", "evidence_codes": ["EVD-CARD-TEXTBOOK-21604E90EA3EDFCC"]}
{"code": "RULE-DDX-0BCDFBDB2EE1", "id": "RULE-DDX-0BCDFBDB2EE1", "name": "STEMI与急性心包炎/心肌炎鉴别规则", "preferred_name": "STEMI与急性心包炎/心肌炎鉴别规则", "display_name": "STEMI与急性心包炎/心肌炎鉴别规则", "entityType": "ClinicalRule", "entityCategory": "CDSS决策规则", "canonical_labels": ["KGNode", "ClinicalRule"], "primary_label": "ClinicalRule", "type_label": "鉴别规则", "rule_category": "differential_point", "rule_type": "鉴别诊断规则", "rule_text": "疑似STEMI如表现为较剧烈且持久的心前区疼痛，同时伴发热，疼痛随呼吸或咳嗽加重，早期可闻及心包摩擦音，心电图表现为除aVR外多导联ST段弓背向下抬高、T波倒置且无异常Q波时，应鉴别急性心包炎/心肌炎。", "original_text": "疑似STEMI如表现为较剧烈且持久的心前区疼痛，同时伴发热，疼痛随呼吸或咳嗽加重，早期可闻及心包摩擦音，心电图表现为除aVR外多导联ST段弓背向下抬高、T波倒置且无异常Q波时，应鉴别急性心包炎/心肌炎。", "evidence_note": "教材STEMI鉴别诊断段落列出急性心包炎/心肌炎的疼痛、发热、心包摩擦音和心电图鉴别特征。", "differential_target_code": "DDX-CARD-A07BA907BDB0", "differential_target_name": "心肌炎", "source_disease_codes": ["DIS-CARD-CM-DCM", "DIS-CARD-CAD-STEMI", "DIS-CARD-CM-RCM", "DIS-CARD-CM-AMYLOID", "DIS-CARD-CM-HCM", "DIS-CARD-CM-ARVC", "DIS-CARD-CM-ACM", "DIS-CARD-CAD-ICM"], "source_disease_names": ["扩张型心肌病", "ST段抬高型心肌梗死", "限制型心肌病", "淀粉样变心肌病", "肥厚型心肌病", "致心律失常性右心室心肌病", "致心律失常性心肌病", "缺血性心肌病"], "scope_type": "心血管内科", "scope_target": "真实鉴别对象规则补齐", "top_specialty": "心血管内科", "batch_id": "BATCH-CARD-DDX-RULE-FILL-20260714-001", "schema_version": "V1.12", "skill_version": "V2.1", "source_type": "authoritative_textbook_or_guideline", "knowledge_layer": "differential_diagnosis_detail", "skeleton_slot": "诊断与鉴别诊断", "clinical_applicability": "diagnosis_support", "review_status": "clinical_ready", "clinical_review_status": "clinical_ready", "formal_cdss_ready": "yes", "merge_status": "server_imported", "conflict_status": "none", "created_at": "2026-07-14 09:58:05", "updated_at": "2026-07-14 09:58:05", "evidence_codes": ["EVD-CARD-TEXTBOOK-21604E90EA3EDFCC"]}
{"code": "RULE-DDX-D0B88EE88ED7", "id": "RULE-DDX-D0B88EE88ED7", "name": "STEMI与急性肺动脉栓塞鉴别规则", "preferred_name": "STEMI与急性肺动脉栓塞鉴别规则", "display_name": "STEMI与急性肺动脉栓塞鉴别规则", "entityType": "ClinicalRule", "entityCategory": "CDSS决策规则", "canonical_labels": ["KGNode", "ClinicalRule"], "primary_label": "ClinicalRule", "type_label": "鉴别规则", "rule_category": "differential_point", "rule_type": "鉴别诊断规则", "rule_text": "胸痛、呼吸困难或休克患者需鉴别STEMI与急性肺动脉栓塞；若伴咯血、晕厥、发绀、P2亢进、颈静脉充盈、右心负荷急性增加、低氧血症，且肺动脉CTA或肺通气/灌注检查异常，应优先考虑肺栓塞；D-二聚体在AMI和肺栓塞中均可升高，不能单独作为鉴别依据。", "original_text": "胸痛、呼吸困难或休克患者需鉴别STEMI与急性肺动脉栓塞；若伴咯血、晕厥、发绀、P2亢进、颈静脉充盈、右心负荷急性增加、低氧血症，且肺动脉CTA或肺通气/灌注检查异常，应优先考虑肺栓塞；D-二聚体在AMI和肺栓塞中均可升高，不能单独作为鉴别依据。", "evidence_note": "教材STEMI鉴别诊断段落包含肺栓塞症状、右心负荷、影像检查和D-二聚体局限性。", "differential_target_code": "DDX-CARD-STEMI-5ED3F170AA98", "differential_target_name": "急性肺动脉栓塞", "source_disease_codes": ["DIS-CARD-CAD-STEMI"], "source_disease_names": ["ST段抬高型心肌梗死"], "scope_type": "心血管内科", "scope_target": "真实鉴别对象规则补齐", "top_specialty": "心血管内科", "batch_id": "BATCH-CARD-DDX-RULE-FILL-20260714-001", "schema_version": "V1.12", "skill_version": "V2.1", "source_type": "authoritative_textbook_or_guideline", "knowledge_layer": "differential_diagnosis_detail", "skeleton_slot": "诊断与鉴别诊断", "clinical_applicability": "diagnosis_support", "review_status": "clinical_ready", "clinical_review_status": "clinical_ready", "formal_cdss_ready": "yes", "merge_status": "server_imported", "conflict_status": "none", "created_at": "2026-07-14 09:58:05", "updated_at": "2026-07-14 09:58:05", "evidence_codes": ["EVD-CARD-TEXTBOOK-21604E90EA3EDFCC"]}
{"code": "RULE-DDX-3B1A851FE970", "id": "RULE-DDX-3B1A851FE970", "name": "STEMI与急腹症鉴别规则", "preferred_name": "STEMI与急腹症鉴别规则", "display_name": "STEMI与急腹症鉴别规则", "entityType": "ClinicalRule", "entityCategory": "CDSS决策规则", "canonical_labels": ["KGNode", "ClinicalRule"], "primary_label": "ClinicalRule", "type_label": "鉴别规则", "rule_category": "differential_point", "rule_type": "鉴别诊断规则", "rule_text": "STEMI可出现上腹痛、恶心呕吐而误诊为急腹症；当存在上腹痛或休克表现时，应结合病史、体格检查、心电图、血清心肌酶和肌钙蛋白动态检测，鉴别急性胰腺炎、消化性溃疡穿孔、急性胆囊炎、胆石症等急腹症。", "original_text": "STEMI可出现上腹痛、恶心呕吐而误诊为急腹症；当存在上腹痛或休克表现时，应结合病史、体格检查、心电图、血清心肌酶和肌钙蛋白动态检测，鉴别急性胰腺炎、消化性溃疡穿孔、急性胆囊炎、胆石症等急腹症。", "evidence_note": "教材STEMI鉴别诊断段落明确急腹症需结合病史、体检、心电图和心肌标志物鉴别。", "differential_target_code": "DDX-CARD-STEMI-F118C9F80AE2", "differential_target_name": "急腹症", "source_disease_codes": ["DIS-CARD-CAD-STEMI"], "source_disease_names": ["ST段抬高型心肌梗死"], "scope_type": "心血管内科", "scope_target": "真实鉴别对象规则补齐", "top_specialty": "心血管内科", "batch_id": "BATCH-CARD-DDX-RULE-FILL-20260714-001", "schema_version": "V1.12", "skill_version": "V2.1", "source_type": "authoritative_textbook_or_guideline", "knowledge_layer": "differential_diagnosis_detail", "skeleton_slot": "诊断与鉴别诊断", "clinical_applicability": "diagnosis_support", "review_status": "clinical_ready", "clinical_review_status": "clinical_ready", "formal_cdss_ready": "yes", "merge_status": "server_imported", "conflict_status": "none", "created_at": "2026-07-14 09:58:05", "updated_at": "2026-07-14 09:58:05", "evidence_codes": ["EVD-CARD-TEXTBOOK-21604E90EA3EDFCC"]}
{"code": "RULE-DDX-F6845CA62524", "id": "RULE-DDX-F6845CA62524", "name": "心肌病与冠心病鉴别规则", "preferred_name": "心肌病与冠心病鉴别规则", "display_name": "心肌病与冠心病鉴别规则", "entityType": "ClinicalRule", "entityCategory": "CDSS决策规则", "canonical_labels": ["KGNode", "ClinicalRule"], "primary_label": "ClinicalRule", "type_label": "鉴别规则", "rule_category": "differential_point", "rule_type": "鉴别诊断规则", "rule_text": "诊断心肌病时，若心肌结构或功能异常可由冠状动脉粥样硬化/心肌缺血充分解释，应优先考虑冠心病或缺血性心肌病；若异常不能由缺血解释，才支持原发或特定类型心肌病。需注意冠心病可与心肌病共存，一种疾病存在不排除另一种疾病。", "original_text": "诊断心肌病时，若心肌结构或功能异常可由冠状动脉粥样硬化/心肌缺血充分解释，应优先考虑冠心病或缺血性心肌病；若异常不能由缺血解释，才支持原发或特定类型心肌病。需注意冠心病可与心肌病共存，一种疾病存在不排除另一种疾病。", "evidence_note": "心肌病指南指出心肌病为高血压、冠状动脉粥样硬化、瓣膜性心脏病等不足以解释的心肌结构/功能异常，且可与缺血性心脏病共存。", "differential_target_code": "DDX-CARD-6AB732E54DB3", "differential_target_name": "冠心病", "source_disease_codes": ["DIS-CARD-CM-ALVC", "DIS-CARD-CAD-ICM", "DIS-CARD-CM-HCM", "DIS-CARD-CM-DCM", "DIS-CARD-CM-AMYLOID", "DIS-CARD-CM-ARVC", "DIS-CARD-CM-ACM"], "source_disease_names": ["致心律失常性左心室心肌病", "缺血性心肌病", "肥厚型心肌病", "扩张型心肌病", "淀粉样变心肌病", "致心律失常性右心室心肌病", "致心律失常性心肌病"], "scope_type": "心血管内科", "scope_target": "真实鉴别对象规则补齐", "top_specialty": "心血管内科", "batch_id": "BATCH-CARD-DDX-RULE-FILL-20260714-001", "schema_version": "V1.12", "skill_version": "V2.1", "source_type": "authoritative_textbook_or_guideline", "knowledge_layer": "differential_diagnosis_detail", "skeleton_slot": "诊断与鉴别诊断", "clinical_applicability": "diagnosis_support", "review_status": "clinical_ready", "clinical_review_status": "clinical_ready", "formal_cdss_ready": "yes", "merge_status": "server_imported", "conflict_status": "none", "created_at": "2026-07-14 09:58:05", "updated_at": "2026-07-14 09:58:05", "evidence_codes": ["EVD-EA12FDB1586C16E92E2D-RCM"]}
{"code": "RULE-DDX-F7863924CD83", "id": "RULE-DDX-F7863924CD83", "name": "心肌病与瓣膜性心脏病鉴别规则", "preferred_name": "心肌病与瓣膜性心脏病鉴别规则", "display_name": "心肌病与瓣膜性心脏病鉴别规则", "entityType": "ClinicalRule", "entityCategory": "CDSS决策规则", "canonical_labels": ["KGNode", "ClinicalRule"], "primary_label": "ClinicalRule", "type_label": "鉴别规则", "rule_category": "differential_point", "rule_type": "鉴别诊断规则", "rule_text": "心肌肥厚、扩大或收缩/舒张功能异常患者，应评估瓣膜狭窄或关闭不全等异常负荷是否足以解释心肌改变；若瓣膜性心脏病足以解释结构功能异常，则不应直接归因于原发心肌病；若两者共存，应分别记录并判断主导病因。", "original_text": "心肌肥厚、扩大或收缩/舒张功能异常患者，应评估瓣膜狭窄或关闭不全等异常负荷是否足以解释心肌改变；若瓣膜性心脏病足以解释结构功能异常，则不应直接归因于原发心肌病；若两者共存，应分别记录并判断主导病因。", "evidence_note": "心肌病指南指出瓣膜性心脏病可能解释心肌结构/功能异常，且可与心肌病共存。", "differential_target_code": "DDX-CARD-645287F85899", "differential_target_name": "瓣膜性心脏病", "source_disease_codes": ["DIS-CARD-CM-RCM", "DIS-CARD-CM-HCM", "DIS-CARD-CM-DCM", "DIS-CARD-CM-ARVC"], "source_disease_names": ["限制型心肌病", "肥厚型心肌病", "扩张型心肌病", "致心律失常性右心室心肌病"], "scope_type": "心血管内科", "scope_target": "真实鉴别对象规则补齐", "top_specialty": "心血管内科", "batch_id": "BATCH-CARD-DDX-RULE-FILL-20260714-001", "schema_version": "V1.12", "skill_version": "V2.1", "source_type": "authoritative_textbook_or_guideline", "knowledge_layer": "differential_diagnosis_detail", "skeleton_slot": "诊断与鉴别诊断", "clinical_applicability": "diagnosis_support", "review_status": "clinical_ready", "clinical_review_status": "clinical_ready", "formal_cdss_ready": "yes", "merge_status": "server_imported", "conflict_status": "none", "created_at": "2026-07-14 09:58:05", "updated_at": "2026-07-14 09:58:05", "evidence_codes": ["EVD-EA12FDB1586C16E92E2D-RCM"]}
{"code": "RULE-DDX-F459BC630CA4", "id": "RULE-DDX-F459BC630CA4", "name": "心肌病与高血压性心脏病鉴别规则", "preferred_name": "心肌病与高血压性心脏病鉴别规则", "display_name": "心肌病与高血压性心脏病鉴别规则", "entityType": "ClinicalRule", "entityCategory": "CDSS决策规则", "canonical_labels": ["KGNode", "ClinicalRule"], "primary_label": "ClinicalRule", "type_label": "鉴别规则", "rule_category": "differential_point", "rule_type": "鉴别诊断规则", "rule_text": "出现心肌肥厚或心功能异常时，应评估长期高血压负荷是否足以解释左室肥厚、舒张功能异常或心衰表现；若高血压性心脏病足以解释异常，应避免误诊为原发心肌病；若证据不足或二者共存，应结合血压病程、影像特征和病因学证据综合判断。", "original_text": "出现心肌肥厚或心功能异常时，应评估长期高血压负荷是否足以解释左室肥厚、舒张功能异常或心衰表现；若高血压性心脏病足以解释异常，应避免误诊为原发心肌病；若证据不足或二者共存，应结合血压病程、影像特征和病因学证据综合判断。", "evidence_note": "心肌病指南指出高血压性心脏病可能解释心肌结构/功能异常，且可与心肌病共存。", "differential_target_code": "DDX-CARD-887CF6C354E7", "differential_target_name": "高血压性心脏病", "source_disease_codes": ["DIS-CARD-CM-RCM", "DIS-CARD-CM-ARVC"], "source_disease_names": ["限制型心肌病", "致心律失常性右心室心肌病"], "scope_type": "心血管内科", "scope_target": "真实鉴别对象规则补齐", "top_specialty": "心血管内科", "batch_id": "BATCH-CARD-DDX-RULE-FILL-20260714-001", "schema_version": "V1.12", "skill_version": "V2.1", "source_type": "authoritative_textbook_or_guideline", "knowledge_layer": "differential_diagnosis_detail", "skeleton_slot": "诊断与鉴别诊断", "clinical_applicability": "diagnosis_support", "review_status": "clinical_ready", "clinical_review_status": "clinical_ready", "formal_cdss_ready": "yes", "merge_status": "server_imported", "conflict_status": "none", "created_at": "2026-07-14 09:58:05", "updated_at": "2026-07-14 09:58:05", "evidence_codes": ["EVD-EA12FDB1586C16E92E2D-RCM"]}
{"code": "RULE-DDX-83832ADF4B3D", "id": "RULE-DDX-83832ADF4B3D", "name": "室上速/房扑与心房颤动鉴别规则", "preferred_name": "室上速/房扑与心房颤动鉴别规则", "display_name": "室上速/房扑与心房颤动鉴别规则", "entityType": "ClinicalRule", "entityCategory": "CDSS决策规则", "canonical_labels": ["KGNode", "ClinicalRule"], "primary_label": "ClinicalRule", "type_label": "鉴别规则", "rule_category": "differential_point", "rule_type": "鉴别诊断规则", "rule_text": "快速性心律失常患者需鉴别心房颤动：房颤心电图表现为P波消失或无明确可重复P波，常以f波代之，且无房室传导阻滞时RR间期绝对不规则；典型房扑则为规律锯齿状F波，房室传导比例可导致心室率规则或不规则。", "original_text": "快速性心律失常患者需鉴别心房颤动：房颤心电图表现为P波消失或无明确可重复P波，常以f波代之，且无房室传导阻滞时RR间期绝对不规则；典型房扑则为规律锯齿状F波，房室传导比例可导致心室率规则或不规则。", "evidence_note": "2025房颤指南定义房颤心电图特征；内科学教材给出房扑F波和传导比例特征。", "differential_target_code": "DDX-CARD-91D172B6AA3C", "differential_target_name": "心房颤动", "source_disease_codes": ["DIS-CARD-ARR-AVNRT", "DIS-CARD-ARR-AFL", "DIS-CARD-ARR-SVT", "DIS-CARD-ARR-AT", "DIS-CARD-ARR-WPW", "DIS-CARD-ARR-AVRT"], "source_disease_names": ["房室结折返性心动过速", "心房扑动", "室上性心动过速", "房性心动过速", "预激综合征", "房室折返性心动过速"], "scope_type": "心血管内科", "scope_target": "真实鉴别对象规则补齐", "top_specialty": "心血管内科", "batch_id": "BATCH-CARD-DDX-RULE-FILL-20260714-001", "schema_version": "V1.12", "skill_version": "V2.1", "source_type": "authoritative_textbook_or_guideline", "knowledge_layer": "differential_diagnosis_detail", "skeleton_slot": "诊断与鉴别诊断", "clinical_applicability": "diagnosis_support", "review_status": "clinical_ready", "clinical_review_status": "clinical_ready", "formal_cdss_ready": "yes", "merge_status": "server_imported", "conflict_status": "none", "created_at": "2026-07-14 09:58:05", "updated_at": "2026-07-14 09:58:05", "evidence_codes": ["EVD-31BFE9E10B3D29C7915D-AF", "EVD-B9CAB7EC30CAB04B08EC-AFL"]}
{"code": "RULE-DDX-A925E1A05CB0", "id": "RULE-DDX-A925E1A05CB0", "name": "房性早搏与房室折返性心动过速触发鉴别规则", "preferred_name": "房性早搏与房室折返性心动过速触发鉴别规则", "display_name": "房性早搏与房室折返性心动过速触发鉴别规则", "entityType": "ClinicalRule", "entityCategory": "CDSS决策规则", "canonical_labels": ["KGNode", "ClinicalRule"], "primary_label": "ClinicalRule", "type_label": "鉴别规则", "rule_category": "differential_point", "rule_type": "鉴别诊断规则", "rule_text": "房性早搏可作为房室折返性心动过速的触发因素：当房性期前收缩下传时旁道仍处不应期而房室结已恢复兴奋性，可经房室结前传、旁道逆传形成折返环。临床展示时应将房性早搏作为触发/鉴别线索，不应误作持续性室上速本体。", "original_text": "房性早搏可作为房室折返性心动过速的触发因素：当房性期前收缩下传时旁道仍处不应期而房室结已恢复兴奋性，可经房室结前传、旁道逆传形成折返环。临床展示时应将房性早搏作为触发/鉴别线索，不应误作持续性室上速本体。", "evidence_note": "教材AVRT机制段落明确房性期前收缩触发顺向型AVRT的机制。", "differential_target_code": "DDX-CARD-F46806C9EB37", "differential_target_name": "房性早搏", "source_disease_codes": ["DIS-CARD-ARR-AFL", "DIS-CARD-ARR-AVRT", "DIS-CARD-ARR-AVNRT", "DIS-CARD-ARR-WPW", "DIS-CARD-ARR-AT", "DIS-CARD-ARR-SVT"], "source_disease_names": ["心房扑动", "房室折返性心动过速", "房室结折返性心动过速", "预激综合征", "房性心动过速", "室上性心动过速"], "scope_type": "心血管内科", "scope_target": "真实鉴别对象规则补齐", "top_specialty": "心血管内科", "batch_id": "BATCH-CARD-DDX-RULE-FILL-20260714-001", "schema_version": "V1.12", "skill_version": "V2.1", "source_type": "authoritative_textbook_or_guideline", "knowledge_layer": "differential_diagnosis_detail", "skeleton_slot": "诊断与鉴别诊断", "clinical_applicability": "diagnosis_support", "review_status": "clinical_ready", "clinical_review_status": "clinical_ready", "formal_cdss_ready": "yes", "merge_status": "server_imported", "conflict_status": "none", "created_at": "2026-07-14 09:58:05", "updated_at": "2026-07-14 09:58:05", "evidence_codes": ["EVD-DA73254797A17F116872-AVRT"]}
{"code": "RULE-DDX-A03E3ED04577", "id": "RULE-DDX-A03E3ED04577", "name": "室上速与窦性心动过速鉴别规则", "preferred_name": "室上速与窦性心动过速鉴别规则", "display_name": "室上速与窦性心动过速鉴别规则", "entityType": "ClinicalRule", "entityCategory": "CDSS决策规则", "canonical_labels": ["KGNode", "ClinicalRule"], "primary_label": "ClinicalRule", "type_label": "鉴别规则", "rule_category": "differential_point", "rule_type": "鉴别诊断规则", "rule_text": "疑似室上性心动过速时需鉴别窦性心动过速：窦速定义为窦性心率>100次/分，I、II、aVF导联P波直立，V1导联双向或倒置；不恰当窦速为排除性诊断，需排除体位性心动过速综合征、窦房结折返性心动过速、局灶性房速以及发热、贫血、疼痛、甲亢等继发因素。", "original_text": "疑似室上性心动过速时需鉴别窦性心动过速：窦速定义为窦性心率>100次/分，I、II、aVF导联P波直立，V1导联双向或倒置；不恰当窦速为排除性诊断，需排除体位性心动过速综合征、窦房结折返性心动过速、局灶性房速以及发热、贫血、疼痛、甲亢等继发因素。", "evidence_note": "室上速专家共识给出窦速定义、心电图特征及不恰当窦速的排除诊断要求。", "differential_target_code": "DDX-CARD-CE220DDF6AA5", "differential_target_name": "窦性心动过速", "source_disease_codes": ["DIS-CARD-ARR-SVT", "DIS-CARD-ARR-AVRT", "DIS-CARD-ARR-AVNRT", "DIS-CARD-ARR-AFL", "DIS-CARD-ARR-AT"], "source_disease_names": ["室上性心动过速", "房室折返性心动过速", "房室结折返性心动过速", "心房扑动", "房性心动过速"], "scope_type": "心血管内科", "scope_target": "真实鉴别对象规则补齐", "top_specialty": "心血管内科", "batch_id": "BATCH-CARD-DDX-RULE-FILL-20260714-001", "schema_version": "V1.12", "skill_version": "V2.1", "source_type": "authoritative_textbook_or_guideline", "knowledge_layer": "differential_diagnosis_detail", "skeleton_slot": "诊断与鉴别诊断", "clinical_applicability": "diagnosis_support", "review_status": "clinical_ready", "clinical_review_status": "clinical_ready", "formal_cdss_ready": "yes", "merge_status": "server_imported", "conflict_status": "none", "created_at": "2026-07-14 09:58:05", "updated_at": "2026-07-14 09:58:05", "evidence_codes": ["EVD-CF7BB456375EF4CC379E-AVNRT"]}
{"code": "RULE-DDX-BB7F299F2DD1", "id": "RULE-DDX-BB7F299F2DD1", "name": "心脏骤停/室颤与癫痫样抽搐鉴别规则", "preferred_name": "心脏骤停/室颤与癫痫样抽搐鉴别规则", "display_name": "心脏骤停/室颤与癫痫样抽搐鉴别规则", "entityType": "ClinicalRule", "entityCategory": "CDSS决策规则", "canonical_labels": ["KGNode", "ClinicalRule"], "primary_label": "ClinicalRule", "type_label": "鉴别规则", "rule_category": "differential_point", "rule_type": "鉴别诊断规则", "rule_text": "心脏骤停或恶性室性心律失常可因脑血流骤降导致意识突然丧失，并伴局部或全身性抽搐，临床不能仅凭抽搐表现判断为癫痫。应同步核查脉搏、呼吸、皮肤颜色、瞳孔、心电监测和复苏反应，优先排除心源性意识丧失。", "original_text": "心脏骤停或恶性室性心律失常可因脑血流骤降导致意识突然丧失，并伴局部或全身性抽搐，临床不能仅凭抽搐表现判断为癫痫。应同步核查脉搏、呼吸、皮肤颜色、瞳孔、心电监测和复苏反应，优先排除心源性意识丧失。", "evidence_note": "教材心脏骤停段落指出心脏骤停后可出现意识突然丧失、局部或全身性抽搐、呼吸停止、皮肤苍白或发绀。", "differential_target_code": "DDX-CARD-E6C98B4ECF84", "differential_target_name": "癫痫", "source_disease_codes": ["DIS-CARD-ARR-VF", "DIS-CARD-SCD-ARREST"], "source_disease_names": ["心室扑动与心室颤动", "心脏骤停"], "scope_type": "心血管内科", "scope_target": "真实鉴别对象规则补齐", "top_specialty": "心血管内科", "batch_id": "BATCH-CARD-DDX-RULE-FILL-20260714-001", "schema_version": "V1.12", "skill_version": "V2.1", "source_type": "authoritative_textbook_or_guideline", "knowledge_layer": "differential_diagnosis_detail", "skeleton_slot": "诊断与鉴别诊断", "clinical_applicability": "diagnosis_support", "review_status": "clinical_ready", "clinical_review_status": "clinical_ready", "formal_cdss_ready": "yes", "merge_status": "server_imported", "conflict_status": "none", "created_at": "2026-07-14 09:58:05", "updated_at": "2026-07-14 09:58:05", "evidence_codes": ["EVD-CARD-DEEP-066B33C52F2F1B"]}
{"code": "RULE-DDX-18B1251FA44C", "id": "RULE-DDX-18B1251FA44C", "name": "预激伴房颤与普通房颤/室颤风险鉴别规则", "preferred_name": "预激伴房颤与普通房颤/室颤风险鉴别规则", "display_name": "预激伴房颤与普通房颤/室颤风险鉴别规则", "entityType": "ClinicalRule", "entityCategory": "CDSS决策规则", "canonical_labels": ["KGNode", "ClinicalRule"], "primary_label": "ClinicalRule", "type_label": "鉴别规则", "rule_category": "differential_point", "rule_type": "鉴别诊断规则", "rule_text": "宽QRS、极不规则快速心律或已知预激患者出现房颤/房扑时，应识别预激伴房颤这一高危情境；其治疗不同于普通房颤，首选电复律或伊布利特/普罗帕酮，避免β受体拮抗剂、维拉帕米、地尔硫䓬、洋地黄类药物和胺碘酮，以免抑制房室结传导、加剧旁道下传并诱发室颤。", "original_text": "宽QRS、极不规则快速心律或已知预激患者出现房颤/房扑时，应识别预激伴房颤这一高危情境；其治疗不同于普通房颤，首选电复律或伊布利特/普罗帕酮，避免β受体拮抗剂、维拉帕米、地尔硫䓬、洋地黄类药物和胺碘酮，以免抑制房室结传导、加剧旁道下传并诱发室颤。", "evidence_note": "教材明确预激伴房颤/房扑的首选处理及禁用药物，指出存在诱发室颤风险。", "differential_target_code": "DDX-CARD-660433DF4D1F", "differential_target_name": "预激综合征伴心房颤动", "source_disease_codes": [], "source_disease_names": [], "scope_type": "心血管内科", "scope_target": "真实鉴别对象规则补齐", "top_specialty": "心血管内科", "batch_id": "BATCH-CARD-DDX-RULE-FILL-20260714-001", "schema_version": "V1.12", "skill_version": "V2.1", "source_type": "authoritative_textbook_or_guideline", "knowledge_layer": "differential_diagnosis_detail", "skeleton_slot": "诊断与鉴别诊断", "clinical_applicability": "diagnosis_support", "review_status": "clinical_ready", "clinical_review_status": "clinical_ready", "formal_cdss_ready": "yes", "merge_status": "server_imported", "conflict_status": "none", "created_at": "2026-07-14 09:58:05", "updated_at": "2026-07-14 09:58:05", "evidence_codes": ["EVD-3C8217C70100704827CC-VF", "EVD-FA19DDD6812364E50C63-VF"]}
